36:06.456 --> 36:08.709
I'm not going to that nursing home.

36:08.959 --> 36:12.921
Green Grove is a retirement community!
It's like a hotel at Captain Teeb's!

36:13.297 --> 36:14.339
Who's he?

36:14.840 --> 36:18.010
A captain who owns luxury hotels
or something.

36:18.218 --> 36:22.890
I talked to Mrs. DiCaprio, and she's
got a corner suite available.

36:23.140 --> 36:25.058
It's available. It'll go fast.

36:25.309 --> 36:27.644
Of course it's available.
Somebody died!

36:28.103 --> 36:33.233
You gotta stop with this black poison
cloud all the time. I can't take it!

36:33.859 --> 36:35.652
Oh, poor you!

36:36.653 --> 36:39.114
I got problems at work,
problems at home.

36:39.364 --> 36:41.825
I got a friend diagnosed with cancer.

36:42.075 --> 36:45.704
Most parents would be grateful
if their children did this!

36:45.954 --> 36:47.748
I'm not going to that place.

36:48.081 --> 36:51.877
I will go to court and get power
of attorney and place you there.

36:52.127 --> 36:53.295
Then kill me now.

36:54.004 --> 36:55.923
Go on, go into the ham...

36:56.340 --> 36:59.551
...and take the carving knife
and stab me here.

36:59.801 --> 37:04.932
Here! Now please, it would hurt me
less than what you just said.

37:05.349 --> 37:07.392
I know seniors that are inspired!

37:17.319 --> 37:20.989
Yo, money, we said we'd meet out
front, and you're not even dressed!

37:21.782 --> 37:22.950
I'm taking a pass.

37:23.742 --> 37:27.454
What? It's Italian suits, Christopher.

37:27.663 --> 37:31.959
There was a time when being with
Tony's crew was all I ever dreamed of.

37:33.168 --> 37:34.253
So what am I doing?

37:34.503 --> 37:36.630
This is some fucking note here.

37:36.838 --> 37:37.923
Don't wake her up.

37:38.173 --> 37:40.300
Come on, it's 5:15.

37:41.218 --> 37:45.180
Maybe one reason things are so fucked
in the organization these days...

37:45.430 --> 37:49.184
...is guys running off not listening
to middle management.

37:49.977 --> 37:52.271
"Fuck Tony." That's a quote.

37:52.521 --> 37:54.773
We have to stick together.

37:55.274 --> 37:57.192
Why be in a crew?

37:57.442 --> 37:58.735
Why be a gangster?

37:59.111 --> 38:00.404
Hey, coach?

38:00.612 --> 38:01.780
Suck my dick.

38:01.947 --> 38:02.948
Yeah.

38:18.130 --> 38:21.925
Yo! Hey! Yo!
We need some help over here!

38:25.679 --> 38:29.391
Okay, let's be very cool, yo!
Get down out of the cab!

38:29.599 --> 38:31.268
You heard the motherfucker.

38:31.476 --> 38:34.646
I'm a friend of Billy's.
Your friend on the inside.

38:34.896 --> 38:37.858
Yeah, cool. "Increase the peace,"
that's our motto.

38:38.442 --> 38:42.112
- I'm gonna take my lunch, okay?
- Yeah, whatever. Come on.

38:46.450 --> 38:49.453
Hold up, man.
You can't drive a Fisher Price.

38:54.499 --> 38:56.918
What's with the gun pointed sideways?

39:03.050 --> 39:06.845
Get out! Come on, get down!
You drive, I'll direct you.

39:11.892 --> 39:13.143
Jesus!

39:13.477 --> 39:15.687
Control your shit, fool!

39:18.982 --> 39:21.943
Fuck, I'm fucked! Fuck!

39:23.653 --> 39:24.905
Fuck!

39:26.698 --> 39:30.369
Fuck! Junior-fucking-Soprano's
gonna go ape-shit. Fuck!

39:32.537 --> 39:35.791
You excited about coming
to live with us, hon?

39:37.626 --> 39:39.211
You will be. Trust me.

39:40.587 --> 39:42.589
Look, Ma, here's your stuff.

39:43.632 --> 39:45.717
- Wow, they made good time.
- Yeah.

39:46.718 --> 39:50.931
You got your own bed and your dresser.

39:51.139 --> 39:54.935
You know, when my grandmother
went to live... elsewhere...

39:55.185 --> 39:58.021
